---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const ayanBreadcrumbData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首页", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "公开课", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/open-class/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "选品竞品矩阵拆解课", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/open-class/competitor-selection-matrix/" }
  ]
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="选品竞品矩阵拆解课 · 公开课详情"
  description="把竞品从看起来好不好做拆成可比较、可记录、可复盘的结构化矩阵，找到你的差异化空间。"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(ayanBreadcrumbData)}></script>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">第 5 节 · 选品竞品矩阵</div>
      <h1>选品竞品矩阵拆解课</h1>
      <p>把竞品从"看起来好不好做"拆成可比较、可记录、可复盘的结构化矩阵。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-label">适合谁</div>
        <div class="info-value">想判断产品能不能做、不知道竞品强不强、想从价格、Review、卖点和痛点里找机会的卖家</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-label">解决什么问题</div>
        <div class="info-value">把竞品从"看起来好不好做"拆成可比较、可记录、可复盘的结构化矩阵。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>课程结构</h2>
      <ol class="step-list">
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">竞品怎么选</div>
            <div class="step-desc">按销量排名选 Top 20，不是按评分。竞品选择决定了矩阵的准确性，选错竞品比不选更危险。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">价格带怎么判断</div>
            <div class="step-desc">把 Top 20 的价格做成散点图，密度最高的区间是红海。找到价格空档，判断自己能否进入。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">Review 数和评分怎么看</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Review 数和评分反映竞争壁垒。高 Review 数 + 高评分 = 强壁垒；高 Review 数 + 低评分 = 用户不满，有机会。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">卖点和差评怎么拆</div>
            <div class="step-desc">卖点词频统计找出"被说烂的卖点"，差评聚合找出"未被满足的需求"。差异化从两者交汇处产生。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">机会点怎么判断</div>
            <div class="step-desc">从价格空档、人群空白、差评痛点、卖点蓝海四个维度交叉判断。机会点需要至少两个维度同时验证。</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>对应文章</h2>
      <div class="related-grid">
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/ai-competitor-matrix/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>用 AI 做竞品矩阵拆解</h3>
          <p>从价格、卖点、人群、痛点四个维度拆解 Top 20 竞品，本节课程的核心方法。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/ai-market-size-estimate/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>AI 做亚马逊市场容量判断</h3>
          <p>判断品类天花板，给竞品矩阵提供"这个池子有多大"的背景数据。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="related-card" href="/articles/selection-pain-reverse/">
          <div class="related-tag">实操文章</div>
          <h3>痛点反推选品 SOP</h3>
          <p>从差评和问答里找真实选品机会，把矩阵输出的机会点落地成产品决策。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>对应资料包</h2>
      <a class="learning-path-card" href="/resources/competitor-selection-matrix/">
        <div class="lp-hint">配套资料</div>
        <h3>选品竞品矩阵</h3>
        <p>四维竞品拆解模板，带学员用真实竞品跑通从选品到矩阵输出的完整流程。</p>
        <span class="lp-cta">查看资料详情 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <h2>资料领取</h2>
      <div class="wechat-block">
        <p>资料详情页会说明领取方式。不确定是否适合？先做 30 秒诊断。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-block">
      <h2>准备开始拆解竞品</h2>
      <p>建议先阅读对应文章，再配合资料包做课后演练。</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a class="cta-primary" href="/resources/competitor-selection-matrix/">查看选品竞品矩阵</a>
        <a class="cta-secondary" href="/open-class/">回到公开课中心</a>
        <a class="cta-secondary" href="/resources/">回到资源中心</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout-amber">
      <strong>⚠ 使用边界</strong>
      <p>竞品矩阵不能替代打样、测款和真实市场验证。矩阵输出的是判断方向，不是选品结论。最终产品决策需要结合供应链能力、资金状况和平台政策综合判断。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 28%, rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.10), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f8fd 0%, #eef3fa 100%);
    padding: 56px 24px 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #eaf2ff;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 42px;
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -1.4px;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 760px;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 34px 24px;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .info-card {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .info-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #b45309;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .info-value {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #1f2937;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .detail-block {
    margin: 0 0 36px;
  }

  .detail-block h2 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .detail-block p {
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .step-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .step-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .step-num {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1368ff, #3b82f6);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .step-body {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .step-desc {
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .related-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .related-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #cfe0ff;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .related-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    background: #eef5ff;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 900;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .related-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #0f172a;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .related-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .learning-path-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff 0%, #f0f7ff 100%);
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .learning-path-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #93c5fd;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.14);
  }

  .lp-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .learning-path-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .learning-path-card p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .lp-cta {
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .wechat-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .wechat-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 32px;
    padding: 0 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #059669;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 13px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .wechat-block p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #065f46;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .cta-block {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-block h2 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.4px;
  }

  .cta-block p {
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 46px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1368ff, #3b82f6);
    color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.22);
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.32);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1368ff;
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #93c5fd;
  }

  .callout-amber {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .callout-amber strong {
    display: block;
    color: #b45309;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .callout-amber p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #57534e;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .related-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
